ly scalable performance. The associated code is available under a BSD-3\nlicense at https://github.com/vanreeslab/murphy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Dec 2021 16:49:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Jul 2022 19:43:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-05"}
